<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="so-conj">so <strong><em>conj</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /səʊ/    美 /soʊ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>因此；所以：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It was late, so we went home.
天晚了，我们就回家了。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>为的是；以便：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Speak clearly, so they may understand you.
说得清楚些，以便他们能听懂你的意思。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>如此说来：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>So, what kind of work do you do?
那么，你是做什么工作的呢？</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="so-that">so that</h3>
<p>1.<strong>为的是；结果是：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We work hard so that we can earn more money.
我们努力工作为的是多赚些钱。</p><footer>北师大⑧ – 24</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He didn’t plan his time well, so that he didn’t finish the work in time. 
他没计划好时间，结果没及时完成工作。</p></div>

<h3 id="so-what">So what?</h3>
<p>1.<strong>那又怎么样？</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Andrew won’t like it, you know.
你知道安德鲁是不会喜欢的。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— So what? I don’t care what Andrew thinks!
那又怎样？我才不在乎安德鲁怎么想呢！</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Cathy had quit her job when her son was born <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (为的是) she could stay home and raise her family.  （2014 浙江改）  </li>
<li>Some animals carry seeds from one place to another, <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (所以) plants can spread to new places.  （2014 北京改）  </li>
<li>— Linda didn’t invite us to the party.
— <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (那又怎样)? I don’t care.  （2011 江苏改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. so that / in order that  2. so  3. So what  </p></div>